    {
      "id": "408c2c7c-3e0a-4a56-baae-d1334fffbb49",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -608,
        1648
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 2240,
        "height": 928,
        "content": "# 🤖 Nano Banana AI Image Editor \n\n## 📋 Workflow Overview\n**Purpose:** Receives photos via Telegram, processes them with AI vision, and sends back analyzed images\n\n## 🔄 Process Flow\n\n1. **📱 Photo Message Receiver**\n   - Listens for incoming Telegram messages with photos\n\n2. **⬇️ Download Telegram Photo**\n   - Fetches the photo file from Telegram servers\n\n3. **🔄 Convert Photo to Base64**\n   - Extracts binary data and converts to Base64 format\n\n4. **🔗 Format Image Data URL**\n   - Creates proper data URL format for AI processing\n\n5. **🧠 Nano Banana Image Processor**\n   - Sends image + caption to Gemini 2.5 Flash via OpenRouter\n   - AI analyzes the image and generates response\n\n6. **📊 Parse AI Response Data**\n   - Extracts image URL and metadata from AI response\n\n7. **💾 Base64 to Binary File**\n   - Converts processed image back to binary format\n\n8. **📤 Send Processed Photo**\n   - Returns the AI-processed image to Telegram chat\n\n## ⚙️ Technical Details\n- **AI Model:** Nano Banana(Gemini 2.5 Flash Image Preview)\n- **API Provider:** OpenRouter (Free tier)\n- **Target Chat ID:** Your chat id\n- **Image Format:** PNG\n\n"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "a04f072e-da6b-4d02-8369-556cfa728aab",
